• app.use("/uploads", express.static(...)) → makes the uploads folder publicly accessible in the browser.

• path.join(__dirname, "uploads") → safely combines the current folder path and "uploads" to create the correct file path.

• Relative path → path based on the current location (example: "uploads/file.jpg").

• Absolute path → full system path from root (example: C:/project/uploads/file.jpg).

